text_raw:
2. The 3rd day of August 2021 is appointed as the day on which Part 3 and 
sections 28 and 31 of the Counterfeiting Act 2021 (No. 16 of 2021) shall come 
into operation. 

GIVEN under my Official Seal, 

26 July, 2021. 

PASCHAL DONOHOE, 
Minister for Finance. 

Notice of the making of this Statutory Instrument was published in 
“Iris Oifigiúil” of 3rd August, 2021.
